<h2 id="parked-mayors-requirements">Parked Mayor’s requirements</h2>

<ol>
  <li>At least 50% affordable housing with no net loss of social rent.</li>
  <li>A full ballot of residents before proceeding with demolition.</li>
  <li>A right to return to the estate for leaseholders and freeholders.</li>
  <li>A late stage viability review/affordable housing clawback.</li>
  <li>Demolition to be considered only as a last resort.</li>
</ol>

